## 7. Data Quality Framework

Quality checks were implemented at both Silver and Gold layers.

### Silver Layer Checks

#### Customer Validation

* Duplicate customer IDs
* Null customer IDs
* Leading/trailing spaces
* Marital status consistency

#### Product Validation

* Duplicate product IDs
* Null product IDs
* Negative product costs
* Invalid product dates

#### Sales Validation

* Invalid dates
* Incorrect sales calculations
* Invalid quantities
* Invalid prices

#### ERP Validation

* Invalid birth dates
* Country standardization
* Category consistency

### Gold Layer Checks

#### Dimension Validation

* Duplicate customer keys
* Duplicate product keys

#### Referential Integrity

* Fact table records without matching dimensions

